task.summary: Default task
Fixes with registration form on email glitch. Added 403, 404, 500 pages. Fix with stackOverFlowException caused by toString() method inside of dao classes.
Minor fixes.
Removed unused tables Address and City, made changes corresponding to the deletion.
Added pagination and logic for it. Made changes in services and controllers in order to fit the pagination.
Changed message that email was sending during the registration. Small fixes with home button.
Fixes with registration fields going red when you autoinput data. Added message boxes with information after registration/confirmation.
Added front-end validation of the registration form. Added real-time login availability check. Added registration submit button loading animation on submit.
Added Sign up link in header tag. Added divider between Log in and Sign up.
Fixes when login and registration boxes were crashing during sizing at particular size.
Started working on the comments. Comments already showing on the page, no availability to post them yet. Fixed some glitches with js, causing site not to respond.
Working on the comments continued.

Fully implemented comments. Admin can delete any comment he want, user can only delete his comments. Small fixes with design in main.css; Fixed typos in About page. Fixed Error caused by lack of @ResponseBody annotation in GlobalExeptionController
Removed unused fields rating and referenced comment from Comment table, implemented changes for that
Small fixes after comment changes.
Started working with film likes/dislikes and bookmarks.
Small css fixes.
Started work on Forgot password function.
Added bookmarks, likes and dislikes to the DB. Created mapping classes for them.
Added BookmarkJSON, BookmarkService.
Fixes when server crashed on start.
Added fully functional bookmarks on films (without bookmarks page).
Added bookmarks to profile page.
Small fixes with with Services causing bad data responses.
Added ability to like and dislike films. Showing liked in the profile section. Added pagination for the films for liked and bookmarked films in profile section.
Fixed an error in JS.
Pagination fix on profile page.

Small fixes with pagination in profile and styles improvement. Huge work made with optimization of calls of Film. Removed unused clientDb's and replaced them with simple Id of Client. Added methods, that are removing load of queries to DB. Changes direct HQL queries to Criterias because of Hibernate support of FetchMode.Join.
Minor fixes with menu in profile page.
Forgot password functionality is fully supported right now, after changing the password, the token is deleted from the DB and the user is given Authority "Anonymous".
Verification token for email is now being deleted from the DB after successful user confirmation.
Grammar of names fixed.
Fully implemented work with users from Admin page. Small fixes with design on Admin panel, fixed problem with favicon.ico. Added 'Back' button to each 'addOrUpdate' page.
Added user administration for Admin to the film page.
Fixes with login mapping.
Added change password ability for the user. Small changes and fixes in the profile. Small fixes with burger in header.
Removed unused favicon. Small changes in services and controllers due to the avatars adding.
Added avatar to profile.
Added user avatar selection for the registration page, small fixes with burger.
Added ability to change avatars from the profile page. Added fully functional user edit. Small fixes and exceptions added in the connected with edit classes. Small styling changes.
Optimised resources loading, fixes with search input in navbar, changes in logic of nav-burger appearance. Small css fixes.
Small fixes
Added search page for mobile use only. Fixed bugs with search on iPhones.
Small changes.
Typos removed.
More fixes with search on mobiles and computers.
Changed ClientDataDb, added field with AiPoints. Added ClientDataService.

Implementation of AI started. Added few services and methods to work with AI. Added new variable to Client_data table with AI points. Added new library to the project to work with the string comparison.
Added method for Combined film comparison with normal film for AI algorithm.
Few fixes with AI algorithm.
